{"tid":354952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如廁無關門被撞釀血案　大陸仔刀傷兩本地男","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T01:21:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57db8fafecedaa5064f0d5f3ff9e99668e6f63ed","tid":354952,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170811/s00001/1442796ecf49a5509e3adc7d6ef66654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170811%2Fs00001%2F1442796ecf49a5509e3adc7d6ef66654.jpg&h=7d8fc2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名內地漢與多名男女友人凌晨2時許光顧深水埗青山道9至15號華懋富臨門大廈地下一間食肆，前往如廁時疑未有關好廁格，一名本地男顧客前往如廁時推開廁門將他撞倒，兩人發生爭執，雙方十多人互相指駡，內地漢撿起一把利刀施襲，兩名本地客的同伴見狀出手制止，反被斬傷，本地客見狀報警。門外遺下大攤血迹，一輛停在路邊的小巴車身沾上血迹，利刀亦遺在小巴車底，警方到場拘捕內地漢。<br />\n<br />\n被捕內地漢姓孫，32歲，腳臉紅腫，孫涉嫌「傷人」罪名，正被扣留調查。據悉，孫持雙程證來港；兩名受刀傷男子均姓梁，分別28歲及30歲，主要頸部受傷，3人清醒送院。至於撞倒孫的28歲姓林本地男子受輕傷，現場接受敷治後拒絕送院，雙方男女返署協助調查，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進。"},{"pid":"60885750523d9a94bda685cbb5978bfffda392ba","tid":354952,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00001/1502413857223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00001%2F1502413857223&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0cce692d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00001%2F1502413857223&h=6680fb67\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00001/1502413857223</a>"},{"pid":"0606fac6f8b79069aea5cbb5d9eed56f9662dc63","tid":354952,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb7c833ec1c2cb07ebbdea0c9d80f3217ccc8ac8","tid":354952,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,